~ Casidy Noteworthy</font></b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ujzonn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jzonn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elder</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(3/13/01 3:15:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=24.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://personal.bhm.bellsouth.net/bhm/r/p/rpo2/Jzonn_Icon.png WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bard's Quest:  A New Beginning</span><hr size=1> Jzonn ponders the words very carefully as he eats his breakfast.  The hot meal begins to settle in his stomache, the coffee is savored as a final cap to the meal.  He leans back in his chair and begins to think of his last trip to the ice land of Velious.  The thought of the numbing cold sends a barely noticable shiver through his body.<br>
<br>
&quot;I've seen this land.  'Tis a cold place with harsh winds and even harsher dangers.  You say you're prohibited from using the magics of the Wizards and Druids?  Does this prohibition extend any further?&quot;<br>
<br>
While he waits for an answer to the question, Jzonn begins to make a checklist in his mind of the things needed for such a journey. <p><B><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE=2 COLOR="#3A6EA5">Jzonn Stormwolf &lt;Final Destiny&gt;</B></FONT><BR>
